<p><strong>云销雨霁</strong><br />
<strong>作者：</strong><span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/timeelapsed" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3662783); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3662783&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1606663842" alt="TimeElapsed" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3662783)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/timeelapsed" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3662783); return false;">TimeElapsed</a></span>，<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/yoghurt-rescuer" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3167340); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3167340&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1606663842" alt="Yoghurt-rescuer" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3167340)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/yoghurt-rescuer" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3167340); return false;">Yoghurt-rescuer</a></span></p>
<p>拨云见日固然大快人心，但这又是以什么代价换来的呢？</p>
<p>是以研究员们互相百合为代价。它不怎么值钱。</p>
<p>抑或是以全体AIC为代价，这与人类命运相比仍不值一提。</p>
<p>感谢<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/breaddddd" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3471238); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3471238&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1606663842" alt="breaddddd" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3471238)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/breaddddd" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3471238); return false;">breaddddd</a></span>的人设图！其遵循cc3.0协议。本文人设皆参照面包人设图进行描写。</p>
<p>本文为“你的鸽子，我来炖”活动的成品文章。</p>
<p>同时，也是基金会galgame其中一条路线的文案。</p>
